The implementation was done in C++using the Polymake [GJ00] software package; its source code can be obtained via https://polymake.org/doku.php/extensions/max mediated sets There are three major parts to the process: (1) Enumerating simplices, (2) classifying simplices, and (3) computing the maximal mediated set.
